{"type":"message","id":"9912a8d2","parentId":"4c1ce743","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:14:22.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想知道如何把 OpenClaw 的心跳默认设置为使用本地千问3.5模型。\n\n我需要：\n1. 查看心跳配置相关的信息\n2. 告诉用户如何修改 HEARTBEAT.md 来让心跳使用千问3.5模型\n\nOpenClaw 的心跳机制是通过 HEARTBEAT.md 文件来配置的。要让心跳使用特定模型，需要：\n1. 在 HEARTBEAT.md 中设置任务\n2. 使用 cron 来调度心跳任务，并指定模型\n\n或者更简单的方法是使用 `cron` 工具来创建一个定时任务，指定使用 ollama/qwen3.5:4b 模型。\n\n让我查看一下 HEARTBEAT.md 的当前状态，然后给出配置建议。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:16","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773803648869}}
