{"type":"message","id":"1b1627ae","parentId":"2c7b1bf2","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:16:49.680Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"✅ 已成功配置 OpenClaw 心跳默认使用本地千问 3.5 模型！\n\n让我再更新一下默认智能体配置，确保 local_helper 使用正确的模型... 实际上从之前的配置看，local_helper 已经是用 ollama/qwen3.5:4b 了。\n\n我应该给用户一个完整的总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **已成功配置 OpenClaw 心跳默认使用本地千问 3.5 模型！**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 配置总结\n\n### 1️⃣ 心跳任务配置 (`HEARTBEAT.md`)\n\n| 配置项 | 值 |\n|--------|-----|\n| **默认模型** | `ollama/qwen3.5:4b` (本地千问3.5) |\n| **健康检查** | 每30分钟执行一次 |\n| **内存监控** | 每小时执行一次 |\n\n### 2️⃣ 智能体模型配置\n\n| 智能体 | 模型 | 状态 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| **main** | `volcengine-plan/kimi-k2.5` | 当前会话使用 |\n| **local_helper** | `ollama/qwen3.5:4b` ✅ | 已配置为本地千问 |\n| **heartbeat** | `ollama/qwen3.5:4b` ✅ | 刚配置完成 |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 工作原理\n\n现在 OpenClaw 心跳系统会：\n\n1. **每隔30分钟** → 千问3.5 检查系统健康状况\n2. **每隔1小时** → 千问3.5 监控内存使用情况\n3. **所有心跳任务** → 默认使用本地千问3.5模型（完全免费，无需API费用）\n\n---\n\n## 💡 优势\n\n| 优势 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **完全免费** | 本地运行，零API调用费用 |\n| **隐私安全** | 数据不上传云端 |\n| **低延迟** | 本地推理，响应更快 |\n| **离线可用** | 无需网络连接 |\n\n配置已完成！下次心跳时就会自动使用千问3.5本地模型了 🎉"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773803760561}}
{"type":"message","id":"8df386c2","parentId":"1b1627ae","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:20:11.363Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-18 11:20:10 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b5495d0535d3cb27699badb36d53]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5495d0535d3cb27699badb36d53\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 11:20 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n查看已有心跳任务"}],"timestamp":1773804011361}}
{"type":"message","id":"8386ad0b","parentId":"8df386c2","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:20:20.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前用户想查看已有的心跳任务。我需要查看 HEARTBEAT.md 文件的内容，以及可能检查 cron 任务列表。\n\n让我先读取 HEARTBEAT.md 文件，然后检查是否有 cron 任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:20","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"cron:21","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","includeDisabled":true}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773804011362}}
{"type":"message","id":"667df616","parentId":"8386ad0b","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:20:20.401Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:20","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - 定时任务配置\n# OpenClaw 心跳任务配置 - 默认使用本地千问 3.5 模型\n\n## 🎯 默认模型设置\ndefault_model: ollama/qwen3.5:4b\n\n## 📝 心跳任务列表\n\ntasks:\n  - name: \"系统健康检查\"\n    schedule: \"every 30m\"  # 每30分钟执行一次\n    model: ollama/qwen3.5:4b\n    prompt: |\n      请检查系统状态并报告：\n      1. 当前时间和日期\n      2. 简要总结当前系统健康状况\n      3. 如果有需要关注的事项，请提醒用户\n      保持回复简洁明了。\n\n  - name: \"内存监控\"\n    schedule: \"every 1h\"  # 每小时执行一次\n    model: ollama/qwen3.5:4b\n    prompt: |\n      请检查内存使用情况：\n      1. 当前内存占用百分比\n      2. 占用内存最多的前3个进程\n      3. 如果内存使用率超过80%，给出优化建议\n\n## 🔄 动态任务（可按需添加）\n# 取消注释下方内容来启用更多任务\n\n# - name: \"每日摘要\"\n#   schedule: \"cron 0 9 * * *\"  # 每天早上9点\n#   model: ollama/qwen3.5:4b\n#   prompt: |\n#     请生成今日摘要：\n#     1. 今日日期和天气\n#     2. 今日待办事项提醒\n#     3. 一条正能量的问候\n\n## 📝 使用说明\n# 1. 所有任务默认使用 ollama/qwen3.5:4b 模型（本地千问3.5）\n# 2. 可以单独为每个任务指定不同的 model\n# 3. schedule 支持: \"every Xm\"(分钟)、\"every Xh\"(小时)、\"cron 表达式\"\n# 4. 修改此文件后，OpenClaw 会在下次心跳时自动加载新配置\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773804020399}}
