{"type":"message","id":"3f5e7932","parentId":"1d7497bd","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:30:07.289Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看来心跳任务还是没有注册到 Cron 调度器中。这可能是因为 HEARTBEAT.md 的格式问题，OpenClaw 可能期望特定的格式。\n\n让我检查一下正确的 HEARTBEAT.md 格式。从配置看，OpenClaw 的 Cron 任务应该通过 `cron` 工具来管理，而不是通过 HEARTBEAT.md 文件。\n\n让我直接通过 `cron add` 来创建心跳任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"心跳任务目前 **还没有注册到 Cron 调度器**（`total: 0`）。\n\n这说明 `HEARTBEAT.md` 文件格式不被 OpenClaw 自动解析为 Cron 任务。让我直接通过 `cron` 工具来创建正确的心跳任务："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"cron:24","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"系统健康检查（千问3.5）","schedule":{"kind":"every","everyMs":1800000},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请检查系统状态并报告：\\n1. 当前时间和日期\\n2. 简要总结当前系统健康状况\\n3. 如果有需要关注的事项，请提醒用户\\n保持回复简洁明了。","model":"ollama/qwen3.5:4b","timeoutSeconds":120},"sessionTarget":"isolated","delivery":{"mode":"announce"},"enabled":true}}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"cron:25","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"内存监控（千问3.5）","schedule":{"kind":"every","everyMs":3600000},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请检查内存使用情况：\\n1. 当前内存占用百分比\\n2. 占用内存最多的前3个进程\\n3. 如果内存使用率超过80%，给出优化建议","model":"ollama/qwen3.5:4b","timeoutSeconds":120},"sessionTarget":"isolated","delivery":{"mode":"announce"},"enabled":true}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773804575856}}
