{"type":"message","id":"6c5ee42a","parentId":"15c8272f","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:30:43.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"✅ 成功创建了两个心跳任务！让我总结一下结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ 心跳任务已成功创建！\n\n我已成功为你创建了两个使用 **本地千问 3.5 模型** 的心跳任务：\n\n---\n\n## 📋 任务清单\n\n| 任务 | 模型 | 频率 | 下次执行 | 任务ID |\n|------|------|------|----------|--------|\n| **系统健康检查（千问3.5）** | `ollama/qwen3.5:4b` | 每30分钟 | 11:40 | `8a5bdbe1-...` |\n| **内存监控（千问3.5）** | `ollama/qwen3.5:4b` | 每小时 | 12:14 | `266c434b-...` |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 任务详情\n\n### 任务1：系统健康检查\n- **执行时间**：每30分钟（11:14 → 11:40 → 12:10 ...）\n- **执行内容**：千问3.5 检查系统状态、时间、健康状况\n- **输出方式**：直接发送到你飞书\n\n### 任务2：内存监控\n- **执行时间**：每小时（11:14 → 12:14 → 13:14 ...）\n- **执行内容**：千问3.5 检查内存占用、Top3进程、优化建议\n- **输出方式**：直接发送到你飞书\n\n---\n\n## 💡 重要提醒\n\n⚠️ **注意内存占用**：Ollama 当前占用了 **5.7GB 内存** 来运行千问3.5模型。\n\n如果内存紧张，你可以：\n1. 等任务执行后，手动停止 Ollama：`ollama stop qwen3.5:4b`\n2. 或者删除这些心跳任务：`cron remove <任务ID>`\n\n---\n\n需要我再添加其他心跳任务，或者帮你查看下次执行的具体时间吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773804607379}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5bb03f3","parentId":"6c5ee42a","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:58:54.018Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-18 12:58:53 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b54975e72e4b8b32b4fdf975f0b4]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54975e72e4b8b32b4fdf975f0b4\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 12:58 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n你好"}],"timestamp":1773809934015}}
{"type":"message","id":"528d35b2","parentId":"e5bb03f3","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:59:05.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户打招呼说\"你好\"，我应该回应。查看一下当前时间（12:58），距离上次对话（11:22）已经过去一段时间了。我应该正常回应用户的问候。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好呀，李跃！👋\n\n好久不见（大概1个半小时）！我刚在后台整理了一些事情。\n\n有什么我可以帮你的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773809934017}}
{"type":"message","id":"c649a5ce","parentId":"528d35b2","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:59:33.763Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-18 12:59:33 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b54975d8acca4b21c9f8f0594034]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54975d8acca4b21c9f8f0594034\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 12:59 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n使用你有什么技巧"}],"timestamp":1773809973760}}
{"type":"message","id":"7049d5a8","parentId":"c649a5ce","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:00:08.105Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"使用你有什么技巧\"，这是一个比较开放的问题。我可以从以下几个方面来回答：\n\n1. 如何更高效地使用我（小妮/OpenClaw助手）\n2. 一些实用的技巧和最佳实践\n3. 如何利用各种技能和功能\n\n让我提供一个全面但实用的回答。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"使用我有好多技巧呢！给你整理一份实用指南 👇\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 核心使用技巧\n\n### 1️⃣ **直接说需求，不用客气**\n- ❌ \"请问你能不能帮我...\"\n- ✅ \"查一下今天的天气\"\n- 我会自动理解并执行\n\n### 2️⃣ **善用技能（Skills）**\n我已经内置了 **40+ 个技能**，比如：\n\n| 技能 | 用途 | 示例 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `web_search` | 搜索网页 | \"搜索 OpenClaw 最新版本\" |\n| `weather` | 查天气 | \"南京今天天气\" |\n| `video-frames` | 视频截图 | \"把视频第10秒截图\" |\n| `image` | 分析图片 | \"描述这张图\" |\n| 飞书系列 | 飞书操作 | \"读一下飞书文档 xxx\" |\n\n### 3️⃣ **子智能体（并行任务）**\n复杂任务可以拆分给子智能体并行处理：\n```\n\"分析这三个文件：file1.js, file2.js, file3.js\"\n```\n我会同时启动多个子智能体分别分析，再汇总结果。\n\n### 4️⃣ **模型切换**\n默认用 Kimi K2.5，但你可以随时指定：\n- \"用千问模型回答\"\n- \"用 DeepSeek 分析这段代码\"\n- \"本地千问3.5运行这个任务\"\n\n---\n\n## 📝 实用场景示例\n\n### 🔍 信息查询\n```\n\"搜索 2024 年 AI 发展趋势\"\n\"总结这篇网页 https://example.com/article\"\n\"南京明天会下雨吗？\"\n```\n\n### 💻 开发辅助\n```\n\"解释这段代码的作用...\"\n\"重构这个函数，让它更简洁\"\n\"找出这段代码的 bug\"\n```\n\n### 📁 文件操作\n```\n\"读取 ~/.bashrc 文件\"\n\"在当前目录创建一个 test.txt，内容为 hello\"\n\"把这段代码保存到 ~/script.js\"\n```\n\n### 🕐 定时任务\n```\n\"每30分钟提醒我看一次邮件\"\n\"每天早上9点给我发今日待办\"\n\"1小时后提醒我开会\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 💡 进阶技巧\n\n1. **连续对话**：我会记住上下文，不用重复说明\n2. **纠正我**：如果理解错了，直接告诉我\"不对，我是想...\"\n3. **多步骤**：复杂任务可以说\"先...然后...最后...\"\n4. **查看状态**：随时问我\"现在有哪些任务在运行\"\n\n---\n\n有什么具体想试试的吗？比如查个天气、搜个资料、或者启动一个定时任务？🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773809973762}}
{"type":"message","id":"d34f581b","parentId":"7049d5a8","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:01:43.184Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-18 13:01:41 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b5497559d0cb0b2dd137040d4afa]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5497559d0cb0b2dd137040d4afa\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 13:01 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n你支持返回一张图片给我么"}],"timestamp":1773810103183}}
{"type":"message","id":"b63d22ce","parentId":"d34f581b","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:02:08.212Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"你支持返回一张图片给我么\" - 问的是我能不能返回图片。\n\n根据我的能力：\n1. 我可以生成图片（使用 DALL-E 或其他图像生成工具，如果配置了的话）\n2. 我可以返回已有的图片文件\n3. 我可以在回复中嵌入图片\n\n但我需要确认当前环境的具体能力。从已有的技能来看，我没有看到专门的图像生成技能，但我可以：\n1. 使用 `image` 工具分析图片\n2. 如果用户要求，我可以尝试生成或返回图片\n\n我应该诚实地回答：我可以返回图片，如果我有图片文件的话。但我不能\"凭空\"生成图片，除非配置了图像生成工具。\n\n让我给出一个实用的回答。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我可以返回图片！支持以下几种方式：\n\n## 📷 我可以做的\n\n| 方式 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **发送已有图片** | 如果你需要我保存的图片文件 | \"把刚才的截图发给我\" |\n| **生成图片** | 通过图像生成工具（需配置） | \"画一只猫\" |\n| **图片分析** | 解读图片内容 | \"这张图里有什么？\" |\n| **截图/录屏** | 使用 `peekaboo` 技能 | \"帮我截个屏\" |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 当前限制\n\n目前环境中**没有配置图像生成工具**（如 DALL-E、Midjourney 等），所以我还不能\"凭空画画\"。\n\n但我可以：\n- 📤 **返回你上传给我的图片**\n- 📸 **帮你截图**（如果你需要）\n- 🔍 **分析图片内容**\n\n---\n\n你想怎么用图片功能？比如：\n- 上传一张图让我分析？\n- 我帮你截个屏幕？\n- 还是有其他需求？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773810103184}}
{"type":"message","id":"884180d3","parentId":"b63d22ce","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:03:22.088Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-18 13:03:21 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b54976f479cb8b281d5b832ae56d]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54976f479cb8b281d5b832ae56d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 13:03 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n有绘画技能么"}],"timestamp":1773810202084}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c2b2b4a","parentId":"884180d3","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:03:32.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问有没有绘画技能。让我检查一下可用的技能列表，看看是否有图像生成相关的技能。\n\n根据之前的技能列表，我看到有：\n- `image` - 图像分析（视觉模型）- 这个是分析图片，不是生成\n- `video-frames` - 视频帧提取\n\n没有看到专门的绘画/图像生成技能，比如 DALL-E、Midjourney、Stable Diffusion 等。\n\n我应该如实告诉用户当前没有绘画技能，但可以：\n1. 搜索并安装绘画技能\n2. 说明当前可用的图像相关功能\n\n让我检查一下 skillhub 是否有绘画相关的技能可用。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"目前没有绘画（图像生成）技能 installed。让我帮你搜索一下有没有可用的绘画技能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:26","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"skillhub search image"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773810202087}}
{"type":"message","id":"686e0889","parentId":"6c2b2b4a","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:03:33.399Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:26","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nimage-and-video-generation-vydra  Image and Video Generation with Vydra API\n  - AI image and video generation via Vydra.ai API. Access Grok Imagine, Gemini, Flux, Veo 3, Kling, and ElevenLabs through one API key. Agents can self-register and generate images automatically.\n基于Vydra.ai API的AI图像视频生成服务，单一密钥集成Grok Imagine、Gemini、Flux、Veo 3、Kling及ElevenLabs，支持智能体自动注册与自动生成图像。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nimage-enhancer  Image Enhancer\n  - Improves the quality of images, especially screenshots, by enhancing resolution, sharpness, and clarity. Perfect for preparing images for presentations, docu...\n提升图像（尤其是截图）的分辨率、锐度与清晰度，适用于演示文稿及文档。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nimage-generate  Image Generate\n  - 使用内置 image_generate.py 脚本生成图片, 准备清晰具体的 `prompt`。\n使用内置 image_generate.py 脚本生成图片, 准备清晰具体的 `prompt`。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nimage-to-video  Image To Video\n  - Still-to-video conversion guide: model selection, motion prompting, and camera movement. Covers Wan 2.5 i2v, Seedance, Fabric, Grok Video with when to use ea...\n图生视频指南：模型选择、运动提示与镜头运动。涵盖Wan 2.5 i2v、Seedance、Fabric、Grok Video及适用场景。\n  - version: 0.1.5\nimage-detection  Image Detection\n  - Analyzes images to detect AI generation, extract metadata, identify artifacts, and perform content moderation using local and cloud-based tools.\n使用本地与云端工具分析图像，检测AI生成、提取元数据、识别伪影并审核内容。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nollama-x-z-image-turbo  Image Generation (Ollama x/z-image-turbo · macOS only)\n  - Génère une image en local via Ollama x/z-image-turbo sur macOS et l'envoie sur WhatsApp selon le prompt donné.\n在 macOS 本地通过 Ollama x/z-image-turbo 根据提示词生成图像并发送至 WhatsApp。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngemini-image-remix  Gemini Image Remix\n  - Generate or remix images using Gemini models with text prompts and multiple input images, supporting various styles, resolutions, and advanced model options.\n使用 Gemini 模型，通过文本提示和多张输入图像生成或重混图片，支持多种风格、分辨率及高级模型选项。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngithub-image-hosting  github-image-hosting\n  - Upload images to img402.dev for embedding in GitHub PRs, issues, and comments. Images under 1MB are uploaded free (no payment, no auth) and persist for 7 days. Use when the agent needs to share an image in a GitHub context — screenshots, mockups, diagrams, or any visual. Triggers: \"screenshot this\", \"attach an image\", \"add a screenshot to the PR\", \"upload this mockup\", or any task producing an image for GitHub.\n上传图片至 img402.dev 以嵌入 GitHub PR、Issue 和评论。1MB 以下免费（免认证），保存 7 天。用于分享截图、原型、图表等视觉内容。触发词：\"截图\"、\"附加图片\"、\"添加截图到 PR\"、\"上传原型\" 或任何生成 GitHub 图片的任务。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen-image-skill  qwenz-image-gen\n  - Generate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\nGenerate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\n  - version: 1.0.0\nseedream-image-for-openclaw  Seedream\n  - 使用火山引擎 Seedream-4.5 API 生成高质量图片。适用于文生图、图生图以及生成关联组图的场景。\n使用火山引擎 Seedream-4.5 API 生成高质量图片。适用于文生图、图生图以及生成关联组图的场景。\n  - version: 0.1.0\nopenclaw-aisa-llm-image-video-qwen-wan26-gemini-3-pro-image  Generate images & videos with: Gemini 3 Pro Image + Qwen Wan 2.6 (video) via one API key\n  - Generate images & videos with AIsa. Gemini 3 Pro Image (image) + Qwen Wan 2.6 (video) via one API key.\n使用AIsa，通过单一API密钥调用Gemini 3 Pro Image（图像）和Qwen Wan 2.6（视频）生成内容。\n  - version: 1.0.0\naliyun-image  aliyun-image\n  - 阿里云百炼图像生成、编辑与翻译。文生图：根据文本生成图像，支持复杂文字渲染。图像编辑：单图编辑、多图融合、风格迁移、物体增删。图像翻译：翻译图像中的文字，保留原始排版，支持11种源语言和14种目标语言。触发词：生成图片、AI作画、文生图、图像编辑、修图、换背景、风格迁移、多图融合、图像翻译、图片翻译。模型：qwen-image-plus(默认)、qwen-image-max、qwen-image-edit-plus(默认)、qwen-image-edit-max、qwen-mt-image。\n阿里云百炼图像生成、编辑与翻译。文生图：根据文本生成图像，支持复杂文字渲染。图像编辑：单图编辑、多图融合、风格迁移、物体增删。图像翻译：翻译图像中的文字，保留原始排版，支持11种源语言和14种目标语言。触发词：生成图片、AI作画、文生图、图像编辑、修图、换背景、风格迁移、多图融合、图像翻译、图片翻译。模型：qwen-image-plus(默认)、qwen-image-max、qwen-image-edit-plus(默认)、qwen-image-edit-max、qwen-mt-image。\n  - version: 1.1.0\nbaoyu-image-gen  Baoyu Image Gen\n  - AI image generation with OpenAI, Google, DashScope and Replicate APIs. Supports text-to-image, reference images, aspect ratios. Sequential by default; parall...\n集成OpenAI、Google、DashScope和Replicate API的AI图像生成，支持文生图、参考图及宽高比设置，默认串行处理。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwenz-image-gen  qwenz-image-gen\n  - Generate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\nGenerate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\n  - version: 1.0.1\nwan-image-video-generation-editting  Wan Image and Video Generation and Editting\n  - Image and Video Generation and Editting wiht Wan series models. It offers text2image, image editting(with prompt), text2video, image2video and reference(imag...\n基于Wan系列模型的图像与视频生成及编辑，支持文生图、图像编辑、文生视频、图生视频及参考生成。\n  - version: 1.0.2\nalicloud-ai-image-qwen-image-edit  Alicloud Ai Image Qwen Image Edit\n  - Edit images with Alibaba Cloud Model Studio Qwen Image Edit models (qwen-image-edit, qwen-image-edit-plus, qwen-image-edit-max and snapshots). Use when modif...\n使用阿里云通义千问图像编辑模型（qwen-image-edit、qwen-image-edit-plus、qwen-image-edit-max及快照版本）编辑图像。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nvolcengine-image-generate  volcengine-image-generate\n  - Using volcengine image_generate.py script to generate image, need to provide clear and specific `prompt`.\n使用火山引擎 image_generate.py 脚本生成图片，需提供清晰具体的提示词。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngrok-imagine-image-pro  Grok Imagine Image Pro\n  - Generates and edits high-quality PNG images via xAI Grok/Flux API using prompts, styles, aspect ratios, and batch processing with base64 output.\n通过 xAI Grok/Flux API 生成编辑高质量 PNG 图像，支持提示词、风格、比例及批量处理，输出 base64 格式。\n  - version: 1.0.2\ntaobao-image-search  Taobao Image Search\n  - 使用淘宝进行以图搜同款、候选比对和加购物车操作。用户提供商品图片并要求“搜同款/找类似款/比价/加入购物车”时使用。优先执行本地脚本（save-taobao-cookie.js、verify-taobao-runner.js）完成全流程；当脚本失败或页面结构变化时回退 browser 工具手动执行。\n使用淘宝进行以图搜同款、候选比对和加购物车操作。用户提供商品图片并要求“搜同款/找类似款/比价/加入购物车”时使用。优先执行本地脚本（save-taobao-cookie.js、verify-taobao-runner.js）完成全流程；当脚本失败或页面结构变化时回退 browser 工具手动执行。\n  - version: 1.0.2\npollinations-image  Pollinations Image Generator\n  - Generate detailed images from text prompts using Pollinations.ai models with optional configuration, model selection, and advanced settings.\n使用 Pollinations.ai 模型根据文本提示生成详细图像，支持配置选项、模型选择和高级设置。\n  - version: 1.0.0"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1219,"aggregated":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nimage-and-video-generation-vydra  Image and Video Generation with Vydra API\n  - AI image and video generation via Vydra.ai API. Access Grok Imagine, Gemini, Flux, Veo 3, Kling, and ElevenLabs through one API key. Agents can self-register and generate images automatically.\n基于Vydra.ai API的AI图像视频生成服务，单一密钥集成Grok Imagine、Gemini、Flux、Veo 3、Kling及ElevenLabs，支持智能体自动注册与自动生成图像。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nimage-enhancer  Image Enhancer\n  - Improves the quality of images, especially screenshots, by enhancing resolution, sharpness, and clarity. Perfect for preparing images for presentations, docu...\n提升图像（尤其是截图）的分辨率、锐度与清晰度，适用于演示文稿及文档。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nimage-generate  Image Generate\n  - 使用内置 image_generate.py 脚本生成图片, 准备清晰具体的 `prompt`。\n使用内置 image_generate.py 脚本生成图片, 准备清晰具体的 `prompt`。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nimage-to-video  Image To Video\n  - Still-to-video conversion guide: model selection, motion prompting, and camera movement. Covers Wan 2.5 i2v, Seedance, Fabric, Grok Video with when to use ea...\n图生视频指南：模型选择、运动提示与镜头运动。涵盖Wan 2.5 i2v、Seedance、Fabric、Grok Video及适用场景。\n  - version: 0.1.5\nimage-detection  Image Detection\n  - Analyzes images to detect AI generation, extract metadata, identify artifacts, and perform content moderation using local and cloud-based tools.\n使用本地与云端工具分析图像，检测AI生成、提取元数据、识别伪影并审核内容。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nollama-x-z-image-turbo  Image Generation (Ollama x/z-image-turbo · macOS only)\n  - Génère une image en local via Ollama x/z-image-turbo sur macOS et l'envoie sur WhatsApp selon le prompt donné.\n在 macOS 本地通过 Ollama x/z-image-turbo 根据提示词生成图像并发送至 WhatsApp。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngemini-image-remix  Gemini Image Remix\n  - Generate or remix images using Gemini models with text prompts and multiple input images, supporting various styles, resolutions, and advanced model options.\n使用 Gemini 模型，通过文本提示和多张输入图像生成或重混图片，支持多种风格、分辨率及高级模型选项。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngithub-image-hosting  github-image-hosting\n  - Upload images to img402.dev for embedding in GitHub PRs, issues, and comments. Images under 1MB are uploaded free (no payment, no auth) and persist for 7 days. Use when the agent needs to share an image in a GitHub context — screenshots, mockups, diagrams, or any visual. Triggers: \"screenshot this\", \"attach an image\", \"add a screenshot to the PR\", \"upload this mockup\", or any task producing an image for GitHub.\n上传图片至 img402.dev 以嵌入 GitHub PR、Issue 和评论。1MB 以下免费（免认证），保存 7 天。用于分享截图、原型、图表等视觉内容。触发词：\"截图\"、\"附加图片\"、\"添加截图到 PR\"、\"上传原型\" 或任何生成 GitHub 图片的任务。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen-image-skill  qwenz-image-gen\n  - Generate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\nGenerate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\n  - version: 1.0.0\nseedream-image-for-openclaw  Seedream\n  - 使用火山引擎 Seedream-4.5 API 生成高质量图片。适用于文生图、图生图以及生成关联组图的场景。\n使用火山引擎 Seedream-4.5 API 生成高质量图片。适用于文生图、图生图以及生成关联组图的场景。\n  - version: 0.1.0\nopenclaw-aisa-llm-image-video-qwen-wan26-gemini-3-pro-image  Generate images & videos with: Gemini 3 Pro Image + Qwen Wan 2.6 (video) via one API key\n  - Generate images & videos with AIsa. Gemini 3 Pro Image (image) + Qwen Wan 2.6 (video) via one API key.\n使用AIsa，通过单一API密钥调用Gemini 3 Pro Image（图像）和Qwen Wan 2.6（视频）生成内容。\n  - version: 1.0.0\naliyun-image  aliyun-image\n  - 阿里云百炼图像生成、编辑与翻译。文生图：根据文本生成图像，支持复杂文字渲染。图像编辑：单图编辑、多图融合、风格迁移、物体增删。图像翻译：翻译图像中的文字，保留原始排版，支持11种源语言和14种目标语言。触发词：生成图片、AI作画、文生图、图像编辑、修图、换背景、风格迁移、多图融合、图像翻译、图片翻译。模型：qwen-image-plus(默认)、qwen-image-max、qwen-image-edit-plus(默认)、qwen-image-edit-max、qwen-mt-image。\n阿里云百炼图像生成、编辑与翻译。文生图：根据文本生成图像，支持复杂文字渲染。图像编辑：单图编辑、多图融合、风格迁移、物体增删。图像翻译：翻译图像中的文字，保留原始排版，支持11种源语言和14种目标语言。触发词：生成图片、AI作画、文生图、图像编辑、修图、换背景、风格迁移、多图融合、图像翻译、图片翻译。模型：qwen-image-plus(默认)、qwen-image-max、qwen-image-edit-plus(默认)、qwen-image-edit-max、qwen-mt-image。\n  - version: 1.1.0\nbaoyu-image-gen  Baoyu Image Gen\n  - AI image generation with OpenAI, Google, DashScope and Replicate APIs. Supports text-to-image, reference images, aspect ratios. Sequential by default; parall...\n集成OpenAI、Google、DashScope和Replicate API的AI图像生成，支持文生图、参考图及宽高比设置，默认串行处理。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwenz-image-gen  qwenz-image-gen\n  - Generate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\nGenerate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\n  - version: 1.0.1\nwan-image-video-generation-editting  Wan Image and Video Generation and Editting\n  - Image and Video Generation and Editting wiht Wan series models. It offers text2image, image editting(with prompt), text2video, image2video and reference(imag...\n基于Wan系列模型的图像与视频生成及编辑，支持文生图、图像编辑、文生视频、图生视频及参考生成。\n  - version: 1.0.2\nalicloud-ai-image-qwen-image-edit  Alicloud Ai Image Qwen Image Edit\n  - Edit images with Alibaba Cloud Model Studio Qwen Image Edit models (qwen-image-edit, qwen-image-edit-plus, qwen-image-edit-max and snapshots). Use when modif...\n使用阿里云通义千问图像编辑模型（qwen-image-edit、qwen-image-edit-plus、qwen-image-edit-max及快照版本）编辑图像。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nvolcengine-image-generate  volcengine-image-generate\n  - Using volcengine image_generate.py script to generate image, need to provide clear and specific `prompt`.\n使用火山引擎 image_generate.py 脚本生成图片，需提供清晰具体的提示词。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngrok-imagine-image-pro  Grok Imagine Image Pro\n  - Generates and edits high-quality PNG images via xAI Grok/Flux API using prompts, styles, aspect ratios, and batch processing with base64 output.\n通过 xAI Grok/Flux API 生成编辑高质量 PNG 图像，支持提示词、风格、比例及批量处理，输出 base64 格式。\n  - version: 1.0.2\ntaobao-image-search  Taobao Image Search\n  - 使用淘宝进行以图搜同款、候选比对和加购物车操作。用户提供商品图片并要求“搜同款/找类似款/比价/加入购物车”时使用。优先执行本地脚本（save-taobao-cookie.js、verify-taobao-runner.js）完成全流程；当脚本失败或页面结构变化时回退 browser 工具手动执行。\n使用淘宝进行以图搜同款、候选比对和加购物车操作。用户提供商品图片并要求“搜同款/找类似款/比价/加入购物车”时使用。优先执行本地脚本（save-taobao-cookie.js、verify-taobao-runner.js）完成全流程；当脚本失败或页面结构变化时回退 browser 工具手动执行。\n  - version: 1.0.2\npollinations-image  Pollinations Image Generator\n  - Generate detailed images from text prompts using Pollinations.ai models with optional configuration, model selection, and advanced settings.\n使用 Pollinations.ai 模型根据文本提示生成详细图像，支持配置选项、模型选择和高级设置。\n  - version: 1.0.0","cwd":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773810213392}}
{"type":"message","id":"66797e96","parentId":"686e0889","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:04:15.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了好多绘画（图像生成）技能！让我给你总结一下：\n\n## 🎨 可用的绘画技能（Image Generation Skills）\n\n### 国内/中文友好的\n| 技能名称 | 说明 | 来源 |\n|---------|------|------|\n| **aliyun-image** | 阿里云百炼图像生成，支持文生图、图像编辑、图像翻译 | 阿里云 |\n| **qwen-image-skill / qwenz-image-gen** | 通义千问图像生成 + 人像照片模型 | 阿里云 |\n| **seedream-image-for-openclaw** | 火山引擎 Seedream-4.5 高质量图像生成 | 火山引擎 |\n| **volcengine-image-generate** | 火山引擎图像生成脚本 | 火山引擎 |\n\n### 国际/多模型\n| 技能名称 | 说明 | 来源 |\n|---------|------|------|\n| **image-and-video-generation-vydra** | Grok Imagine、Gemini、Flux、Veo 3、Kling、ElevenLabs | Vydra.ai |\n| **pollinations-image** | Pollinations.ai 模型图像生成 | Pollinations |\n| **grok-imagine-image-pro** | xAI Grok/Flux API 高质量图像 | xAI |\n| **gemini-image-remix** | Gemini 图像生成和重混 | Google |\n| **baoyu-image-gen** | OpenAI、Google、DashScope、Replicate API | 多平台 |\n| **openclaw-aisa-llm-image-video** | Gemini 3 Pro Image + Qwen Wan 2.6 (video) | AIsa |\n\n### 本地/隐私\n| 技能名称 | 说明 | 来源 |\n|---------|------|------|\n| **ollama-x-z-image-turbo** | 本地 Ollama x/z-image-turbo 生成（macOS only） | 本地 |\n| **image-generate** | 内置 image_generate.py 脚本生成 | 内置 |\n\n### 其他\n| 技能名称 | 说明 |\n|---------|------|\n| **image-enhancer** | 图像质量增强（分辨率、锐度、清晰度） |\n| **image-to-video** | 图生视频（Wan 2.5 i2v、Seedance、Fabric、Grok Video） |\n| **image-detection** | 图像检测（AI生成检测、元数据提取、内容审核） |\n| **wan-image-video-generation-editting** | Wan 系列模型图像视频生成编辑 |\n| **alicloud-ai-image-qwen-image-edit** | 阿里云千问图像编辑 |\n| **taobao-image-search** | 淘宝以图搜同款 |\n| **github-image-hosting** | 图片上传到 img402.dev 用于 GitHub |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 推荐安装\n\n如果你想用中文友好的：\n\n```bash\nskillhub install aliyun-image          # 阿里云百炼\nskillhub install qwen-image-skill      # 通义千问\nskillhub install seedream-image-for-openclaw  # 火山引擎\n```\n\n如果想用国际的：\n\n```bash\nskillhub install pollinations-image    # 免费，无需API Key\nskillhub install grok-imagine-image-pro # xAI Grok\n```\n\n如果注重隐私（本地）：\n\n```bash\nskillhub install ollama-x-z-image-turbo  # 本地运行，macOS only\n```\n\n---\n\n你想安装哪个？或者想让我帮你搜索更多特定功能的绘画技能？🎨","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你搜索并安装一个绘画技能！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:27","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"skillhub search image | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773810213402}}
