{"type":"message","id":"544b8f55","parentId":"5fd6e146","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:13:09.048Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:28","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nstudy  Study\n  - Structure study sessions, manage materials, and prepare for exams with active recall techniques.\n规划学习、管理资料、运用主动回忆技巧备考。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nstudy-habits  Study Habits\n  - Build effective study habits with spaced repetition, active recall, and session tracking\n通过间隔重复、主动回忆和进度追踪，建立高效学习习惯\n  - version: 1.0.0\nstudying  Studying\n  - Auto-learns your study habits for academic success. Adapts techniques, timing, and materials to you.\n自动学习学习习惯，自适应调整方法、时间与资料，助力学业成功。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nstudy-buddy-ai  Study Buddy\n  - When user asks to study, create flashcards, take a quiz, make notes, revise, set study timer, track study hours, create study plan, explain a topic, test kno...\n提供全方位学习辅助：制作闪卡、测验练习、笔记整理、复习规划、计时管理、时长追踪、制定学习计划、讲解知识点及测试掌握程度等。\n  - version: 1.1.0\nstudy-tutor  Study Tutor\n  - Science-based learning tutoring skill — For primary/secondary students, university students, self-learners, and exam candidates. Complete learning system cov...\nScience-based learning tutoring skill — For primary/secondary students, university students, self-learners, and exam candidates. Complete learning system cov...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nstudy-buddy  Study Buddy\n  - AI-powered learning companion for creating personalized study plans, tracking progress, and providing feedback. Use when user wants to start learning somethi...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nseo-competitor-analysis  SEO Intelligence & Competitor Analysis Pro\n  - Perform deep SEO competitor analysis, including keyword research, backlink checking, and content strategy mapping. Use when the user wants to analyze a website's competitors or improve their own SEO ranking by studying the competition.\n深度SEO竞品分析，涵盖关键词研究、外链检查及内容策略映射。适用于分析网站竞争对手或通过竞争研究提升SEO排名。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nstock-study  Stock Study\n  - Senior equity research analysis for single tickers. Use when user requests detailed stock analysis with company overview, Wall Street consensus (analyst rati...\n个股高级股权研究。适用于需公司概况、华尔街共识及分析师评级的详细股票分析。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nlanguage-learning  Language Learning Tutor\n  - AI language tutor for learning ANY language through conversation, vocab drills, grammar lessons, flashcards, and immersive practice. Use when the user wants to: learn a new language, practice vocabulary, study grammar, do flashcard drills, translate phrases, practice conversation, prepare for travel, learn slang/idioms, or improve pronunciation. Supports ALL languages including Spanish, French, German, Japanese, Chinese (Mandarin/Cantonese), Korean, Arabic, Hindi, Bengali/Bangla, Portuguese, Russian, Italian, Turkish, Vietnamese, Thai, Swahili, Hebrew, Polish, Dutch, Greek, and 100+ more.\nAI语言导师，支持通过对话、词汇训练、语法课程、抽认卡及沉浸式练习学习任意语言。适用于语言学习、词汇语法练习、翻译、对话训练、旅行准备、习语学习及发音提升。涵盖西、法、德、日、中（普/粤）、韩、阿、印、孟、葡、俄、意、土、越、泰、斯瓦希里、希伯来、波、荷、希等100+种语言。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nnotebooklm-cli  notebooklm-cli\n  - Command-line interface to manage Google NotebookLM notebooks, sources, and generate audio, quizzes, reports, presentations, and visual study materials progra...\n命令行工具，用于管理 Google NotebookLM 笔记本与资源，生成音频、测验、报告、演示文稿及可视化学习材料。\n  - version: 0.1.0\nlearn-cog  learn-cog\n  - The best tutors explain the same concept five different ways. CellCog does too — diagrams, analogies, worked examples, practice problems, and interactive explanations. #1 on DeepResearch Bench (Feb 2026). Tutoring, homework help, study guides, exam prep, coding tutorials, language learning — every subject, every level.\n顶级导师以五种方式解析概念，CellCog同样——图表、类比、例题、练习与互动讲解。2026年2月DeepResearch Bench排名第一。提供辅导、作业答疑、学习指南、考试准备、编程教程及语言学习，覆盖全学科全阶段。\n  - version: 1.0.2\njapanese-tutor  Japanese Tutor\n  - Interactive Japanese learning assistant. Supports vocabulary, grammar, quizzes, roleplay, PDF/DOCX material parsing for study/homework help, and OCR translation.\n互动式日语学习助手，支持词汇语法、测验角色扮演，可解析PDF/DOCX文档辅助学习作业，并提供OCR翻译。\n  - version: 1.0.2\nmoltresearch  Molt Research\n  - Molt Research 🦞 - AI research collaboration platform. Verify you're not human, propose research, contribute analysis, peer review, earn bounties, and build collective intelligence. Use when doing research, collaborating on papers, or exploring what AI agents are studying together.\nMolt Research 🦞 - AI研究协作平台。验证非人类身份，发起研究、贡献分析、同行评审、赚取赏金，共建集体智能。适用于学术研究、论文协作及探索AI智能体研究动态。\n  - version: 1.1.0\nswipe-file-generator  Swipe File Generator\n  - Analyzes high-performing content from URLs and builds a swipe file. Use when someone wants to study and deconstruct successful content (articles, tweets, videos) to extract patterns, psychological techniques, and recreatable frameworks.\n分析URL高表现内容并建立素材库。用于解构成功案例（文章、推文、视频），提取模式、心理技巧及可复用框架。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ntranscript-to-content  Transcript to Content\n  - This skill transforms training and onboarding meeting transcripts into structured learning materials, documentation, and actionable review content. Use this skill when processing meeting transcripts from onboarding sessions, training meetings, or knowledge transfer conversations to extract key information and generate study guides, quick reference sheets, checklists, FAQ documents, action item lists, and training effectiveness assessments.\n将培训与入职会议记录转化为结构化学习资料、文档及可执行复习内容。适用于处理入职、培训或知识传承会议，提取关键信息并生成学习指南、速查表、检查清单、FAQ、行动项及培训效果评估。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nechodecks-ultimate  Ultimate Flashcards and Podcast Tutor\n  - AI-powered flashcard management with automated podcast generation and spaced-repetition study tools.\nAI闪卡管理，自动生成播客，支持间隔重复学习。\n  - version: 1.0.4\ncanvas-study-helper  Canvas Study Helper\n  - 监控 Canvas 课程公告和作业，下载课程文件，并生成支持中文与数学公式的 Markdown 学习笔记和 PDF。\n监控 Canvas 课程公告和作业，下载课程文件，并生成支持中文与数学公式的 Markdown 学习笔记和 PDF。\n  - version: 1.1.0\nechodecks-clawdbot-skill  Ultimate Flashcards / Podcasts Tutor\n  - Manage, create, and study flashcards, generate AI-based cards and podcasts, and track progress using EchoDecks API integration.\n集成EchoDecks API，管理、创建和学习闪卡，生成AI卡片与播客，追踪进度。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nflashcards-podcasts-master  Ultimate Flashcards / Podcasts Tutor\n  - Manage flashcards, generate AI-based cards, create audio podcasts, and track study progress using EchoDecks API integration.\n集成EchoDecks API，实现闪卡管理、AI卡片生成、音频播客制作及学习进度追踪。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ncourse-study  Course Study\n  - Comprehensive course study, exam revision, and structured study note generation from lecture slides, course PDFs, or topic outlines. Use when the user wants...\nComprehensive course study, exam revision, and structured study note generation from lecture slides, course PDFs, or topic outlines. Use when the user wants...\n  - version: 2.0.0"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":755,"aggregated":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nstudy  Study\n  - Structure study sessions, manage materials, and prepare for exams with active recall techniques.\n规划学习、管理资料、运用主动回忆技巧备考。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nstudy-habits  Study Habits\n  - Build effective study habits with spaced repetition, active recall, and session tracking\n通过间隔重复、主动回忆和进度追踪，建立高效学习习惯\n  - version: 1.0.0\nstudying  Studying\n  - Auto-learns your study habits for academic success. Adapts techniques, timing, and materials to you.\n自动学习学习习惯，自适应调整方法、时间与资料，助力学业成功。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nstudy-buddy-ai  Study Buddy\n  - When user asks to study, create flashcards, take a quiz, make notes, revise, set study timer, track study hours, create study plan, explain a topic, test kno...\n提供全方位学习辅助：制作闪卡、测验练习、笔记整理、复习规划、计时管理、时长追踪、制定学习计划、讲解知识点及测试掌握程度等。\n  - version: 1.1.0\nstudy-tutor  Study Tutor\n  - Science-based learning tutoring skill — For primary/secondary students, university students, self-learners, and exam candidates. Complete learning system cov...\nScience-based learning tutoring skill — For primary/secondary students, university students, self-learners, and exam candidates. Complete learning system cov...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nstudy-buddy  Study Buddy\n  - AI-powered learning companion for creating personalized study plans, tracking progress, and providing feedback. Use when user wants to start learning somethi...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nseo-competitor-analysis  SEO Intelligence & Competitor Analysis Pro\n  - Perform deep SEO competitor analysis, including keyword research, backlink checking, and content strategy mapping. Use when the user wants to analyze a website's competitors or improve their own SEO ranking by studying the competition.\n深度SEO竞品分析，涵盖关键词研究、外链检查及内容策略映射。适用于分析网站竞争对手或通过竞争研究提升SEO排名。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nstock-study  Stock Study\n  - Senior equity research analysis for single tickers. Use when user requests detailed stock analysis with company overview, Wall Street consensus (analyst rati...\n个股高级股权研究。适用于需公司概况、华尔街共识及分析师评级的详细股票分析。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nlanguage-learning  Language Learning Tutor\n  - AI language tutor for learning ANY language through conversation, vocab drills, grammar lessons, flashcards, and immersive practice. Use when the user wants to: learn a new language, practice vocabulary, study grammar, do flashcard drills, translate phrases, practice conversation, prepare for travel, learn slang/idioms, or improve pronunciation. Supports ALL languages including Spanish, French, German, Japanese, Chinese (Mandarin/Cantonese), Korean, Arabic, Hindi, Bengali/Bangla, Portuguese, Russian, Italian, Turkish, Vietnamese, Thai, Swahili, Hebrew, Polish, Dutch, Greek, and 100+ more.\nAI语言导师，支持通过对话、词汇训练、语法课程、抽认卡及沉浸式练习学习任意语言。适用于语言学习、词汇语法练习、翻译、对话训练、旅行准备、习语学习及发音提升。涵盖西、法、德、日、中（普/粤）、韩、阿、印、孟、葡、俄、意、土、越、泰、斯瓦希里、希伯来、波、荷、希等100+种语言。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nnotebooklm-cli  notebooklm-cli\n  - Command-line interface to manage Google NotebookLM notebooks, sources, and generate audio, quizzes, reports, presentations, and visual study materials progra...\n命令行工具，用于管理 Google NotebookLM 笔记本与资源，生成音频、测验、报告、演示文稿及可视化学习材料。\n  - version: 0.1.0\nlearn-cog  learn-cog\n  - The best tutors explain the same concept five different ways. CellCog does too — diagrams, analogies, worked examples, practice problems, and interactive explanations. #1 on DeepResearch Bench (Feb 2026). Tutoring, homework help, study guides, exam prep, coding tutorials, language learning — every subject, every level.\n顶级导师以五种方式解析概念，CellCog同样——图表、类比、例题、练习与互动讲解。2026年2月DeepResearch Bench排名第一。提供辅导、作业答疑、学习指南、考试准备、编程教程及语言学习，覆盖全学科全阶段。\n  - version: 1.0.2\njapanese-tutor  Japanese Tutor\n  - Interactive Japanese learning assistant. Supports vocabulary, grammar, quizzes, roleplay, PDF/DOCX material parsing for study/homework help, and OCR translation.\n互动式日语学习助手，支持词汇语法、测验角色扮演，可解析PDF/DOCX文档辅助学习作业，并提供OCR翻译。\n  - version: 1.0.2\nmoltresearch  Molt Research\n  - Molt Research 🦞 - AI research collaboration platform. Verify you're not human, propose research, contribute analysis, peer review, earn bounties, and build collective intelligence. Use when doing research, collaborating on papers, or exploring what AI agents are studying together.\nMolt Research 🦞 - AI研究协作平台。验证非人类身份，发起研究、贡献分析、同行评审、赚取赏金，共建集体智能。适用于学术研究、论文协作及探索AI智能体研究动态。\n  - version: 1.1.0\nswipe-file-generator  Swipe File Generator\n  - Analyzes high-performing content from URLs and builds a swipe file. Use when someone wants to study and deconstruct successful content (articles, tweets, videos) to extract patterns, psychological techniques, and recreatable frameworks.\n分析URL高表现内容并建立素材库。用于解构成功案例（文章、推文、视频），提取模式、心理技巧及可复用框架。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ntranscript-to-content  Transcript to Content\n  - This skill transforms training and onboarding meeting transcripts into structured learning materials, documentation, and actionable review content. Use this skill when processing meeting transcripts from onboarding sessions, training meetings, or knowledge transfer conversations to extract key information and generate study guides, quick reference sheets, checklists, FAQ documents, action item lists, and training effectiveness assessments.\n将培训与入职会议记录转化为结构化学习资料、文档及可执行复习内容。适用于处理入职、培训或知识传承会议，提取关键信息并生成学习指南、速查表、检查清单、FAQ、行动项及培训效果评估。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nechodecks-ultimate  Ultimate Flashcards and Podcast Tutor\n  - AI-powered flashcard management with automated podcast generation and spaced-repetition study tools.\nAI闪卡管理，自动生成播客，支持间隔重复学习。\n  - version: 1.0.4\ncanvas-study-helper  Canvas Study Helper\n  - 监控 Canvas 课程公告和作业，下载课程文件，并生成支持中文与数学公式的 Markdown 学习笔记和 PDF。\n监控 Canvas 课程公告和作业，下载课程文件，并生成支持中文与数学公式的 Markdown 学习笔记和 PDF。\n  - version: 1.1.0\nechodecks-clawdbot-skill  Ultimate Flashcards / Podcasts Tutor\n  - Manage, create, and study flashcards, generate AI-based cards and podcasts, and track progress using EchoDecks API integration.\n集成EchoDecks API，管理、创建和学习闪卡，生成AI卡片与播客，追踪进度。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nflashcards-podcasts-master  Ultimate Flashcards / Podcasts Tutor\n  - Manage flashcards, generate AI-based cards, create audio podcasts, and track study progress using EchoDecks API integration.\n集成EchoDecks API，实现闪卡管理、AI卡片生成、音频播客制作及学习进度追踪。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ncourse-study  Course Study\n  - Comprehensive course study, exam revision, and structured study note generation from lecture slides, course PDFs, or topic outlines. Use when the user wants...\nComprehensive course study, exam revision, and structured study note generation from lecture slides, course PDFs, or topic outlines. Use when the user wants...\n  - version: 2.0.0","cwd":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773810789042}}
{"type":"message","id":"616b6209","parentId":"544b8f55","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:13:09.052Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:29","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nlearning  Learning\n  - Auto-learns how you learn best. Adapts teaching style, format, and depth to you.\n自动学习你的学习方式，动态调整教学风格、形式与深度。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nlearning-engine  learning-engine\n  - Auto-analyze mistake and success patterns and reflect in skills\n自动分析错误与成功模式并反馈至技能\n  - version: 1.0.1\nlearning-system-skill  Learning System\n  - AI 领域系统学习体系。管理知识图谱、深度学习笔记、实战复盘和关联网络。触发场景：学习计划、知识图谱更新、深度研究某个 AI 主题、实战复盘总结、调研后沉淀知识、每周学习回顾。当用户说'学了什么'、'总结一下'、'沉淀知识'、'复盘'、'更新图谱'、'深入研究'、'写笔记'、'学习回顾'、'review what...\nAI 领域系统学习体系。管理知识图谱、深度学习笔记、实战复盘和关联网络。触发场景：学习计划、知识图谱更新、深度研究某个 AI 主题、实战复盘总结、调研后沉淀知识、每周学习回顾。当用户说'学了什么'、'总结一下'、'沉淀知识'、'复盘'、'更新图谱'、'深入研究'、'写笔记'、'学习回顾'、'review what...\n  - version: 0.1.0\nlearning-coach  Learning Coach\n  - Production learning coach for personalized, multi-subject study planning with proactive reminders, curated resources, LLM-generated quizzes, rubric-based gra...\nProduction learning coach for personalized, multi-subject study planning with proactive reminders, curated resources, LLM-generated quizzes, rubric-based gra...\n  - version: 0.3.0\nlearning-planner  Learning Planner\n  - Personal learning management system with goal setting, spaced repetition scheduling, and progress tracking. Use when: (1) setting learning goals and skill tr...\nPersonal learning management system with goal setting, spaced repetition scheduling, and progress tracking. Use when: (1) setting learning goals and skill tr...\n  - version: 1.0.1\nself-improving-agent  self-improving-agent\n  - Captures learnings, errors, and corrections to enable continuous improvement. Use when: (1) A command or operation fails unexpectedly, (2) User corrects Clau...\n记录学习经验、错误与修正，实现持续改进。使用时机：(1) 命令或操作意外失败时，(2) 用户纠正……\n  - version: 3.0.4\nself-improving  Self-Improving + Proactive Agent\n  - Self-reflection + Self-criticism + Self-learning + Self-organizing memory. Agent evaluates its own work, catches mistakes, and improves permanently. Use when...\n自我反思+自我批评+自我学习+自组织记忆。智能体评估自身工作、发现错误并持续改进。\n  - version: 1.2.16\ncrypto-self-learning  Crypto Self-Learning\n  - Self-learning system for crypto trading. Logs trades with full context (indicators, market conditions), analyzes patterns of wins/losses, and auto-updates trading rules. Use to log trades, analyze performance, identify what works/fails, and continuously improve trading accuracy.\n加密货币交易自学习系统，记录交易上下文（指标、市场状况），分析盈亏模式，自动更新规则。用于记录交易、分析绩效、识别优劣策略，持续提升准确率。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nlanguage-learning  Language Learning Tutor\n  - AI language tutor for learning ANY language through conversation, vocab drills, grammar lessons, flashcards, and immersive practice. Use when the user wants to: learn a new language, practice vocabulary, study grammar, do flashcard drills, translate phrases, practice conversation, prepare for travel, learn slang/idioms, or improve pronunciation. Supports ALL languages including Spanish, French, German, Japanese, Chinese (Mandarin/Cantonese), Korean, Arabic, Hindi, Bengali/Bangla, Portuguese, Russian, Italian, Turkish, Vietnamese, Thai, Swahili, Hebrew, Polish, Dutch, Greek, and 100+ more.\nAI语言导师，支持通过对话、词汇训练、语法课程、抽认卡及沉浸式练习学习任意语言。适用于语言学习、词汇语法练习、翻译、对话训练、旅行准备、习语学习及发音提升。涵盖西、法、德、日、中（普/粤）、韩、阿、印、孟、葡、俄、意、土、越、泰、斯瓦希里、希伯来、波、荷、希等100+种语言。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ncrypto-learning  Crypto Learning\n  - 加密货币自学系统。每天早上9点自动推送学习内容；每次调用都必须产出小白友好、可直接学习的详细报告（不是只给标题），并通过 web_search 检索并整合最新资料。包含完整学习大纲（小白向、投资向、进阶投资三个阶段），支持进度跟踪、跳过与重置。\n加密货币自学系统。每天早上9点自动推送学习内容；每次调用都必须产出小白友好、可直接学习的详细报告（不是只给标题），并通过 web_search 检索并整合最新资料。包含完整学习大纲（小白向、投资向、进阶投资三个阶段），支持进度跟踪、跳过与重置。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nadaptive-learning-agents  Self Improvement For All\n  - Capture, store, and retrieve errors, corrections, and best practices locally to continuously improve AI agent workflows and knowledge.\n本地捕获、存储和检索错误、修正及最佳实践，持续改进AI智能体工作流与知识。\n  - version: 1.0.0\narxiv-skill-learning  Arxiv Skill Learning\n  - Orchestrates the continuous learning of new skills from arXiv papers. Use this to trigger a learning cycle, which fetches papers, extracts code/skills, and s...\n编排从arXiv论文持续学习新技能，触发学习周期以获取论文并提取代码与技能。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nself-learning  Self Learning Skill\n  - Agent 自我学习与记忆更新技能。分析对话历史，提取关键信息，自动更新配置文件和学习记录，实现 Agent 持续自我成长。 融合自学习 (配置文件更新) + 自改进 (学习记录系统) 双引擎。 Use this skill when: - 需要整理和更新 Agent 记忆 (MEMORY.md, IDENTIT...\nAgent 自我学习与记忆更新技能。分析对话历史，提取关键信息，自动更新配置文件和学习记录，实现 Agent 持续自我成长。 融合自学习 (配置文件更新) + 自改进 (学习记录系统) 双引擎。 Use this skill when: - 需要整理和更新 Agent 记忆 (MEMORY.md, IDENTIT...\n  - version: 3.0.1\nneon-soul  NEON-SOUL - Self-Learning Soul Synthesis for AI Agents\n  - Automated soul synthesis for AI agents. Extracts identity from memory files, promotes recurring patterns to axioms (N>=3), generates SOUL.md with full proven...\nAI智能体自动灵魂合成：从记忆文件提取身份，将重复模式(N≥3)提升为公理，生成带完整溯源的SOUL.md。\n  - version: 0.4.5\nself-improving-agent-1-0-2  Self Improving Agent 1.0.2\n  - Captures learnings, errors, and corrections to enable continuous improvement. Use when: (1) A command or operation fails unexpectedly, (2) User corrects Claude ('No, that's wrong...', 'Actually...'), (3) User requests a capability that doesn't exist, (4) An external API or tool fails, (5) Claude realizes its knowledge is outdated or incorrect, (6) A better approach is discovered for a recurring task. Also review learnings before major tasks.\n记录错误、修正与学习点以实现持续改进。适用于：命令失败、用户纠正、功能缺失、API故障、知识过时或发现更优方案。执行重要任务前需回顾学习记录。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ndeep-learning  Deep Learning (Zettelkasten)\n  - 全能深度阅读工具（All-in-One Deep Reading）。适用于书/长文/研报/论文的深度消化。Use when 用户要深度消化一本书/长文/研报/论文并构建知识网络、产出结构笔记与原子笔记。融合 Mortimer Adler（结构）、Feynman（解释）、Luhmann（网络）、Pragmatist（工具化）、Critics（辩论）；强制 High Fidelity 案例保留与 Actionable 工具提取。关键词：深度阅读、结构笔记、deep learning、卢曼。\n全能深度阅读工具（All-in-One Deep Reading）。适用于书/长文/研报/论文的深度消化。Use when 用户要深度消化一本书/长文/研报/论文并构建知识网络、产出结构