{"type":"message","id":"0b8b6950","parentId":"91fb26f8","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:50:22.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，用户要求我安装 `ima-skills` 技能，并提供了 API Key 和 Client ID。我已经：\n\n1. 保存了 API 凭证到 `~/.openclaw/.env`\n2. 设置了环境变量\n3. 创建了技能目录和基本文件（SKILL.md、_meta.json、ima_api.sh）\n\n但我还需要创建一个 tools.json 文件，这是技能的核心配置文件，定义了这个技能提供哪些工具。让我完成它。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:44","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ima-skills/tools.json","content":"{\n  \"tools\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"ima_note_search\",\n      \"description\": \"搜索 IMA 笔记，支持按标题或正文搜索\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"search_type\": {\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"description\": \"搜索类型：0=标题检索（默认），1=正文检索\",\n            \"enum\": [0, 1],\n            \"default\": 0\n          },\n          \"query\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"搜索关键词\"\n          },\n          \"start\": {\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"description\": \"起始偏移量，默认 0\",\n            \"default\": 0\n          },\n          \"end\": {\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"description\": \"结束偏移量，默认 20\",\n            \"default\": 20\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"query\"]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"ima_note_list_folders\",\n      \"description\": \"列出所有笔记本（文件夹）\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"cursor\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"分页游标，首次传 \\\"0\\\"\",\n            \"default\": \"0\"\n          },\n          \"limit\": {\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"description\": \"每页数量，默认 20\",\n            \"default\": 20\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"ima_note_list\",\n      \"description\": \"列出指定笔记本中的笔记\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"folder_id\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"笔记本 ID，为空则列出全部笔记\"\n          },\n          \"cursor\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"分页游标，首次传空字符串\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"limit\": {\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"description\": \"每页数量，默认 20\",\n            \"default\": 20\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"ima_note_read\",\n      \"description\": \"读取指定笔记的详细内容\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"doc_id\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"笔记 ID（docid）\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"doc_id\"]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"ima_note_create\",\n      \"description\": \"创建新笔记\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"content\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"笔记内容（Markdown 格式）\"\n          },\n          \"folder_id\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"目标笔记本 ID（可选，为空则创建到默认位置）\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"content\"]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"ima_note_append\",\n      \"description\": \"向已有笔记追加内容\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"doc_id\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"笔记 ID\"\n          },\n          \"content\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"要追加的内容（Markdown 格式）\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"doc_id\", \"content\"]\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773812959690}}
