{"type":"message","id":"4b80f84e","parentId":"2dbbbc95","timestamp":"2026-03-18T05:51:11.715Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我创建 package.json 和一个简单的 README 来完成这个技能：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:45","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ima-skills/package.json","content":"{\n  \"name\": \"ima-skills\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"腾讯 IMA 笔记管理技能 - 通过 OpenAPI 管理 IMA 智能工作台笔记\",\n  \"main\": \"ima_api.sh\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"ima\", \"tencent\", \"notes\", \"笔记\", \"腾讯\"],\n  \"author\": \"iampennyli\",\n  \"license\": \"MIT\",\n  \"repository\": {\n    \"type\": \"git\",\n    \"url\": \"https://clawhub.ai/iampennyli/ima-skills\"\n  }\n}\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:46","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ima-skills/README.md","content":"# IMA Skills - 腾讯 IMA 笔记管理\n\n通过 IMA OpenAPI 管理腾讯 IMA 智能工作台的笔记，支持读取（搜索、列表、获取内容）和写入（新建、追加）。\n\n## 配置\n\n需要设置环境变量：\n\n```bash\nexport IMA_OPENAPI_CLIENTID=\"your_client_id\"\nexport IMA_OPENAPI_APIKEY=\"your_api_key\"\n```\n\n获取地址：https://ima.qq.com/agent-interface\n\n## 功能\n\n### 搜索笔记\n- 按标题或正文内容搜索\n- 支持分页\n\n### 浏览笔记本\n- 列出所有笔记本\n- 查看笔记本中的笔记列表\n\n### 读取笔记\n- 获取笔记详细内容\n- 支持纯文本格式\n\n### 创建笔记\n- 新建 Markdown 格式笔记\n- 可指定目标笔记本\n\n### 追加内容\n- 向已有笔记追加内容\n- 支持 Markdown 格式\n\n## 使用示例\n\n```bash\n# 搜索笔记\n./ima_api.sh search 0 \"关键词\" 0 20\n\n# 列出笔记本\n./ima_api.sh list_folders \"0\" 20\n\n# 读取笔记\n./ima_api.sh read \"doc_id\"\n\n# 创建笔记\n./ima_api.sh create \"# 标题\\n\\n内容\"\n\n# 追加内容\n./ima_api.sh append \"doc_id\" \"\\n## 补充内容\"\n```\n\n## 接口文档\n\n完整的数据结构和接口参数详见腾讯 IMA 官方文档。\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 笔记内容属于用户隐私，在群聊场景中只展示标题和摘要，禁止展示笔记正文\n- 时间字段是 Unix 毫秒时间戳\n- 内容写入前必须确保为 UTF-8 编码\n- 笔记内容有大小上限，超过时需拆分为多次追加\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773813022663}}
