{"type":"message","id":"ef3d1769","parentId":"04745a72","timestamp":"2026-03-18T06:32:18.042Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"配置已成功更新到 OpenClaw 主配置文件中！✅\n\n## 📝 配置更新摘要\n\n### 添加的配置项\n\n```json\n\"tools\": {\n  \"agentToAgent\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"allow\": [\"main\", \"local_host\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 配置说明\n\n| 属性 | 值 | 说明 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| `enabled` | `true` | ✅ 启用智能体间通信 |\n| `allow` | `[\"main\", \"local_host\"]` | 允许 `main` 和 `local_host` 智能体相互通信 |\n\n### 功能意义\n\n此配置允许：\n- **主智能体** (`main`) 与 **本地辅助智能体** (`local_host`) 之间进行直接通信\n- 实现更复杂的分布式任务处理\n- 支持智能体间的协同工作和信息共享\n\n配置已生效，无需重启服务！🎉\n\n需要我帮你查看或修改其他配置吗？","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置已成功更新到 OpenClaw 主配置文件中！✅\n\n## 📝 配置更新摘要\n\n### 添加的配置项\n\n```json\n\"tools\": {\n  \"agentToAgent\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"allow\": [\"main\", \"local_host\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 配置说明\n\n| 属性 | 值 | 说明 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| `enabled` | `true` | ✅ 启用智能体间通信 |\n| `allow` | `[\"main\", \"local_host\"]` | 允许 `main` 和 `local_host` 智能体相互通信 |\n\n### 功能意义\n\n此配置允许：\n- **主智能体** (`main`) 与 **本地辅助智能体** (`local_host`) 之间进行直接通信\n- 实现更复杂的分布式任务处理\n- 支持智能体间的协同工作和信息共享\n\n配置已生效，无需重启服务！🎉\n\n需要我帮你查看或修改其他配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773815510424}}
{"type":"message","id":"97c855e9","parentId":"ef3d1769","timestamp":"2026-03-18T06:37:41.493Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-18 14:37:40 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b5490cd8d10a0b4b04161019315f]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5490cd8d10a0b4b04161019315f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 14:37 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n如何清理上下文"}],"timestamp":1773815861490}}
{"type":"message","id":"68bcc558","parentId":"97c855e9","timestamp":"2026-03-18T06:39:02.792Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问如何清理上下文。这是一个关于OpenClaw会话管理的问题。\n\n清理上下文通常意味着：\n1. 清除会话历史/记忆\n2. 重置上下文窗口\n3. 删除记忆文件\n4. 重启会话\n\n我应该提供几种清理上下文的方法，从简单到复杂。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"清理上下文有几种方式，取决于你想清理到什么程度：\n\n## 🧹 清理方式（由轻到重）\n\n### 1️⃣ **轻量清理** — 重置当前会话上下文\n```bash\n# 在当前会话中执行\n/reset\n```\n这会清除当前对话的短期记忆，但保留记忆文件。\n\n---\n\n### 2️⃣ **中度清理** — 删除特定记忆文件\n\n| 文件 | 作用 | 删除命令 |\n|------|------|---------|\n| `MEMORY.md` | 长期记忆 | `rm ~/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md` |\n| `memory/*.md` | 每日记忆 | `rm ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/*.md` |\n| `AGENTS.md` | 代理配置 | `rm ~/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md` |\n\n---\n\n### 3️⃣ **深度清理** — 重置整个会话\n\n```bash\n# 1. 删除会话历史\nrm -rf ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*\n\n# 2. 重置工作区状态\nrm ~/.openclaw/workspace/.openclaw/workspace-state.json\n\n# 3. 重启 OpenClaw Gateway\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4️⃣ **完全重置** — 从头开始 ⚠️\n\n```bash\n# 备份重要配置\ncp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json ~/openclaw-backup.json\n\n# 删除整个配置目录（谨慎！）\nrm -rf ~/.openclaw/*\n\n# 重新初始化\nopenclaw onboard\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 推荐方案\n\n**如果只是对话太长了**：\n```bash\n/reset\n```\n\n**如果想忘掉之前的任务/记忆**：\n```bash\nrm ~/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n```\n\n**如果想彻底重新开始**：\n```bash\nrm -rf ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/* && openclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n你想清理到什么程度？我可以帮你执行具体的命令。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773815861492}}
